        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[哆啦A梦害怕]#淋巴结肿大是什么原因#】淋巴结是人体正常的免疫结构，在感染、炎症、肿瘤等病理状态时，淋巴细胞会迅速增生，导致淋巴结肿大。#如何区分淋巴结...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦害怕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_03haipa-32e9b53caf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%8B%E5%B7%B4%E7%BB%93%E8%82%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%8B%E5%B7%B4%E7%BB%93%E8%82%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#淋巴结肿大是什么原因#</span></a>】淋巴结是人体正常的免疫结构，在感染、炎症、肿瘤等病理状态时，淋巴细胞会迅速增生，导致淋巴结肿大。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E6%B7%8B%E5%B7%B4%E7%BB%93%E8%82%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8E%E6%B7%8B%E5%B7%B4%E7%98%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E6%B7%8B%E5%B7%B4%E7%BB%93%E8%82%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8E%E6%B7%8B%E5%B7%B4%E7%98%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#如何区分淋巴结肿大与淋巴瘤#</span></a>：①局部淋巴结肿大多跟感染有关，但全身性的淋巴结肿大要引起重视；②肿瘤性淋巴结触感较硬且按着不痛，按着疼且皮肤局部发红时，多数是炎症性淋巴结；③通过淋巴结活检做最终定性👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4974411116118030" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hkf4cflvsyj60p80xmtuw02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ha7wQGY7lx08aCyqm0Gs01041200s7oy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701580501&amp;ssig=ix7EuTWn%2FQ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/OixrXNy0lx08aCyrtf8Y01041200ghAX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701580501&amp;ssig=KAv5cDI2VQ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Z1POg1rQlx08aCyrxkFW0104120090DF0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701580501&amp;ssig=Y5%2F0XvyY6W&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4974411116118030" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
